OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1775146264
OL,3,CFrench teenager flown to Southampton
OL,4,Cafter traffic collision
OL,6,FThe States of Jersey Police is
OL,7,Fappealing for information after a
OL,8,Fteenage girl was involved in a road
OL,9,Ftraffic collision on Wednesday 1 April.
OL,11,FPolice say a 14-year-old girl was
OL,12,Fvisiting the island from France before
OL,13,Fbeing involved in a collision between
OL,14,F5:10pm and 5:15pm on La Route des
OL,15,FGenets, just outside the Les Ruisseaux
OL,16,FEstate.
OL,18,FThe incident involved a grey Honda
OL,19,FCRV, driven by a 70-year-old man, and
OL,20,Fleft the girl with serious head
OL,21,Finjuries.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
