PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1775146264
OL,3,CFrench teenager flown to Southampton
OL,4,Cafter traffic collision
OL,6,FPolice say no other people or vehicles
OL,7,Fwere involved, and while no arrests
OL,8,Fhave been made, the incident is still
OL,9,Funder investigation.
OL,11,FParamedics treated the girl at the
OL,12,Fscene before being transported to
OL,13,FJersey Hospital.
OL,15,FWhile her condition was described as
OL,16,Fserious but stable, the girl was
OL,17,Furgently flown to Southampton for
OL,18,Fongoing treatment due to the
OL,19,Fseriousness of the head injury.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
