OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1775146264
OL,3,CFrench teenager flown to Southampton
OL,4,Cafter traffic collision
OL,6,FPolice now say that she is in a more
OL,7,Fstable condition.
OL,9,FLa Route des Genets was closed for
OL,10,Fseveral hours while police
OL,11,Finvestigated the scene. Main roads
OL,12,Freopened after 9pm.
OL,14,FJersey's police force is now asking
OL,15,Ffor anyone who may have seen the car,
OL,16,Fthe collision, or has dashcam footage
OL,17,Fto come forward.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
